      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is subject to a documented software quality assurance plan including version control, regression test suite (1200+ test cases), and ISO 9001-certified release process. All simulation scripts are stored in a Git repository with tagged releases corresponding to each analysis run. SQA records reviewed and found compliant with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
